Diakonos
--------

Place the diakonos.conf file in /usr/local/share/diakonos/ or ~/.diakonos/.
The diakonos program can be run from anywhere, such as ~/bin/ or /usr/local/bin/.

Send comments, feedback and tech support requests to irc.freenode.net:6667#geobot
or http://purepistos.net/forums .

Pistos
http://purepistos.net/diakonos